          <title>Luka Doncic has triple-double with season-best 45 points in Mavs' 143-133 win over Warriors</title>
          <description><![CDATA[SAN FRANCISCO (AP) — Luka Doncic had his 80th career triple-double with a season-high 45 points along with 13 assists and 11 rebounds, and the Dallas Mavericks beat Klay Thompson's former Golden State Warriors 143-133 on Sunday night in a second visit to Chase Center in just more than a month.]]></description>
